description: Reserved Matters Application for layout, scale, design, appearance, access and landscaping pursuant to conditions B1, B8, Q1 and A4 of the Stratford City Outline Planning Permission (ref: 10/90641/EXTODA) comprising the construction of buildings including two towers of up to a maximum height of 29 storeys (115m AOD) and 24 together with associated podium buildings ranging from 7 and 10 storeys respectively to provide 422 residential units with associated parking for cars, motorcycles, cycles and mobility scooters at basement, vehicular access from Anthems Way, and provision of Local Equipped Area of Play on Ravens Walk.
